---
title: Easy Dijon Chicken Orecchiette  with Veggies & Parsley
description: Are you thinking the same thing we are? Is it that dijon mustard would go so well as a sauce for juicy chicken? Well then, let’s not wait around, dive in and cook up a creamy pasta to test out our new theory because we know it’s going to be a success.
